data.text:
Cllr. Dr. Aoibhinn Tormey was selected as a Fine Gael General Election Candidate for Dublin Bay North in the upcoming General Election.

She represents the Howth Malahide Ward on Fingal County Council which includes Howth, Sutton, Bayside, Baldoyle, Kinsealy, Balgriffin, Portmarnock, and Malahide. She is the Fine Gael group leader on Fingal County Council, chairperson of the Howth Malahide Area Committee, and member of the Dublin North East Regional Health Forum.
